Interface VCSHistoryProvider.ParentProvider

  • Enclosing interface:
    VCSHistoryProvider

    public static interface VCSHistoryProvider.ParentProvider
    Implement and pass over to a VCSHistoryProvider.HistoryEntry in case you want VCSHistoryProvider.HistoryEntry.getParentEntry(VCSFileProxy) to return relevant values.
